* '''Player:''' Sorry, I'm still looking.

===Talking to Tenzing===
* {{tact|Standard dialogue options}}
* {{topt|Do you know where I can find Trollweiss?}}
** '''Player:''' Do you know where I can find Trollweiss?
** '''Tenzing:''' It has been a long time since someone has asked me about Trollweiss.
** '''Tenzing:''' In the old days Trollweiss could be found all over the mountains, but recently it has been disappearing!
** '''Tenzing:''' There is one place, where I am sure it still grows, but it is impossible to get to.
** '''Player:''' Nothing's impossible, if you put your mind to it!
** '''Tenzing:''' Ahhh, the youth of today. So sure of their prowess. But who am I to stop you from walking into your doom, if that is what you wish to do!
** '''Player:''' Spare me with the lectures and tell me where to find this flower!
** '''Tenzing:''' Well, you will need to enter the domain of the ice trolls! This is an area full of wicked beasts and biting cold. From there you will find a way down a slope to a plateau where the Trollweiss grows.
** '''Tenzing:''' It used to be easy to get to this plateau, but it is now snowed over and virtually inaccessible. That's global warming for you!
** '''Player:''' There must be a way to get there.
** '''Tenzing:''' There is maybe one thing...
** '''Player:''' Go on.
** '''Tenzing:''' If you could make some sort of sled, you could probably get down there but I don't know where that would lead you, as you will not be able to go up the mountain again.
** {{topt|That doesn't sound like a very good idea to me!}}
*** '''Player:''' That doesn't sound like a very good idea to me!
*** '''Tenzing:''' Pah, who are you to talk? Without me you would never have found the secret path to the plateau!!
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|What would I need to make such a sled?}}
*** '''Player:''' What would I need to make such a sled?
*** '''Tenzing:''' Well, I'm no expert. Maybe you should speak to someone who knows more about such technical stuff.
*** '''Player:''' Like who?
*** '''Tenzing:''' Why don't you ask Dunstan. He's always helped me with my spiked boots.
*** '''Player:''' Thank you very much for the information.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|I've got to go.}}
*** '''Player:''' I've got to go.
*** '''Tenzing:''' See you later
*** {{tact|end}}

